These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: german, thai, egyptian, australian
4 different pets are kept: bird, ferret, goldfish, pony
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, ice-hockey, lacrosse, water-polo
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: begonia, bellflower, lily, orchid
 1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is not to the right of the person who's sport is cycling##8
 2. the person who growsbegonia is not to the left of the person who growsbegonia##8
 3. the person who growsorchid is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's sport is cycling is not to the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##8
 5. the person who growsbegonia is not to the right of the person who growsbegonia##8
 6. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 7. the thai is somewhere to the right of the german##5
 8. the owner of the pony is between the person who growsbellflower and the person who's sport is ice-hockey##2
 9. the person who growsorchid is the owner of the goldfish##1
10. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the australian##1
11. the egyptian is on the left or right of the owner of the bird##3
12. the australian is somewhere to the right of the thai##5
13. the owner of the goldfish is not to the left of the person who growsorchid##8
14. the thai is the person who growslily##1
15. the thai is not the person who's sport is ice-hockey##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Nationality         | german     | thai   | australian | egyptian |
| Pet   | ferret | pony   | bird   | goldfish  |
| Sport         | ice-hockey  | lacrosse  | water-polo  | cycling |
| Flower     | begonia    | lily | bellflower     | orchid    |

