.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: ivory, emerald, light-blue, brown
There 4 different types of food: carrot, grapes, kale, peas
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, water-polo, snowboarding, rowing
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, van, trike, subway
 1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is between the person driving the motorbike and the person who's sport is water-polo##2
 2. the person who likes emerald is not to the right of the person driving the van##8
 3. the person who likes emerald is on the left or right of the person eating carrot##3
 4. the person who likes ivory is not to the right of the person driving the subway##8
 5. the person driving the motorbike is not to the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##8
 6. the person eating peas is not to the right of the person who likes brown##8
 7. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the left of the person driving the subway##5
 8. the person driving the trike is in an odd position##4
 9. the person who's sport is climbing is the person driving the van##1
10. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left or right of the person driving the motorbike##3
11. the person driving the motorbike is not to the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##8
12. the person who likes brown is on the left of the person who likes emerald##1
13. the person who's sport is rowing is somewhere to the right of the person eating grapes##5
14. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left or right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##3
15. the person who likes ivory is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person eating kale is on the right of the person eating carrot##1
17. the person who likes ivory is not to the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##8
18. the person eating grapes is not to the right of the person driving the van##8
19. the person who likes brown is on the right of the person eating grapes##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| Color      | ivory | light-blue | brown  | emerald  |
| Food          | peas     | grapes | carrot | kale  |
| Sport   | water-polo    | snowboarding  | rowing | climbing |
| Transport           | trike | subway | motorbike    | van  |

