.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, card-games, skydiving, sudoku
There 4 different types of food: pear, potato, nectarine, pineapple
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: orchid, aconite, daisy, sunflower
City: marseilles, san-francisco, edinburgh, venice
 1. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
 2. the person who's hobby is card-games is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##5
 3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the left of the person eating pineapple##5
 4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere to the right of the person who growsorchid##5
 5. the person traveling to edinburgh is not to the right of the person eating pear##8
 6. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not to the left of the person eating nectarine##8
 7. the person who growsdaisy is in an odd position##4
 8. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1
 9. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the person eating potato##1
10. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the far right##1
11. the person eating pear is not to the left of the person who growsaconite##8
12. the person eating pineapple is on the left or right of the person traveling to san-francisco##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | camping    | sudoku   | skydiving | card-games |
| Food   | pear     | nectarine  | pineapple   | potato      |
