 9. the mexican is on the right of the software-developer##1
10. the electrician is the person traveling to colone##1
11. the person traveling to london is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in september##8
12. the dancer is on the left or right of the person traveling to london##3
13. the pakistani is on the right of the thai##1
14. the electrician is on the left or right of the person traveling to london##3
