 5. the person who's birthday is in may is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 6. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##8
 7. the person drinking sprite is not the person who's hobby is board-games##6
 8. the person eating lemon is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in may and the person drinking sprite##7
 9. the person who's birthday is in may is somewhere to the right of the person eating lemon##5
10. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the person eating lemon##3
11. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person eating grapefruit##1
12. the person eating lemon is not the person who's hobby is baking##6
13. the person who's hobby is gardening is somewhere to the right of the person drinking sprite##5
14. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
