.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-16::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: lily, marigold, begonia, daffodil
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, hiking, gardening, magic-tricks
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, cycling, lacrosse, tennis
4 different games are played: snooker, whist, bridge, monopoly
 1. the person who growsbegonia is the person who's sport is tennis##1
 2. the person playing whist is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
 3. the person who growsmarigold is somewhere to the right of the person playing monopoly##5
 4. the person who growslily is on the far left##1
 5. the person playing snooker is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##3
 6. the person playing bridge is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is gardening##3
 7. the person who growsmarigold is on the left or right of the person who growsbegonia##3
 8. the person playing whist is not to the right of the person who's sport is cycling##8
 9. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
10. the person who growsmarigold is not to the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##8
11. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
12. the person playing monopoly is in an odd position##4
13. the person who's hobby is gardening is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cycling##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Flower      | lily   | daffodil     | begonia    | marigold |
| Hobby   | cooking  | magic-tricks      | gardening     | hiking     |
| Sport         | climbing | lacrosse  | tennis     | cycling  |
| Game     | snooker     | bridge | monopoly | whist     |

